query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'electronics',
'magento',
'mathoverflow',
'serverfault')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('algebraic-groups',
'cart',
'circuit-design',
'command-line',
'configurable-product',
'differential-equations',
'finite-groups',
'integrated-circuit',
'memory',
'powershell',
'rf',
'st.statistics')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Editor',
'Informed',
'Popular Question',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Tumbleweed') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
